snippet.title: Aquaventure (Atari 2600)
snippet.description:
Name: Aquaventure 
Company: Atari
Model #: Unknown
Programmer: Gary Shannon & Tod Frye
Year: 1983
Released? No
Notes: Aquaventure may have originally been called Sea Sentinel
